        public static org.apache.calcite.util.Pair<org.apache.calcite.rex.RexNode,org.apache.calcite.rex.RexNode> extractPartitionPredicates(org.apache.calcite.plan.RelOptCluster cluster,
                                                                                                                                     RelOptHiveTable hiveTable,
                                                                                                                                     org.apache.calcite.rex.RexNode predicate)
        Breaks the predicate into 2 pieces. The first piece is the expressions that only contain partition columns and can be used for Partition Pruning; the second piece is the predicates that are left.
        Parameters:
        cluster -
        hiveTable -
        predicate -
        Returns:
        a Pair of expressions, each of which maybe null. The 1st predicate is expressions that only contain partition columns; the 2nd predicate contains the remaining predicates.
